  "detailed_description": "Doctor Ian Smith, a lieutenant in the <i>HMS Justice</i>, has the bad luck of meeting a pirate ship on his last journey before leaving the Royal Navy. When he learns the name of his captor, a certain Captain \"Bloody Henry\" Plank, his luck takes a turn for the worse... or maybe not.<br><br><strong><i>Jolly Roger</i></strong> is a BL romance in a pirate setting, around 5k words long. Rating: SFW.<br><br>-Character art: Aielia Poot<br><br>-Backgrounds: Minikle<br><br>-Project managing, Writing, and Spanish translation: Ertal",
